  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">7 Security of Your Personally Identifiable Information We use a variety of industry-standard security technologies and procedures to help protect your PersonallyIdentifiable Information from unauthorized access use or disclosure We also require you to enter a password to access your registration information Please do not disclose your registration password to unauthorized people No method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure however Therefore while Hearst uses reasonable efforts to protect your Personally Identifiable Information Hearst cannot guarantee its absolute security</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

